---

All of the translations in this repository that are specified in the
`swarm_translate/scenarios` directory are in the public domain with a CC0
license. The model(s) used, timestamps, and source texts are documented in the
associated output files (respective output file names are specified in the
scenario files).

To the best of our knowledge, the output translations are fully unique
translations of the source texts, not relying on any existing translations other
than the source texts themselves.
